, 174.2273, 174.2984, 174.966, 174.5825, 175.6569, 176.184, 175.9906, 175.6363, 175.417, 174.9124, 175.4479, 176.2265, 175.8788, 176.4513, 176.963, 178.2598, 176.9818, 176.5012, 176.5409, 175.9525, 175.004, 175.421, 174.7861, 175.1106, 174.5959, 174.0493, 173.5997, 174.138, 173.4055, 172.7663, 172.1835, 172.6558, 173.5046, 173.6678, 174.5334, 174.9291, 175.0535, 176.066, 177.0673, 177.3154, 178.2194, 178.276, 178.6766, 178.8411, 178.9845, 177.7977, 178.2258, 178.3694, 178.6448, 178.3998, 178.76, 178.0518, 177.7413, 178.8176, 179.9898, 178.5424, 178.3026, 179.901, 179.4658, 179.1627, 179.7379, 179.5864, 178.2372, 177.7899, 177.8311, 177.2073, 177.6627, 177.2958, 175.5344, 175.2794, 175.3661, 176.3341, 176.7491, 177.3336, 178.2222, 177.9181, 178.4323, 177.5745, 177.7304, 178.5344, 178.0125, 179.3018, 178.6824, 177.5141, 177.6427, 177.0358, 177.9054, 177.9316, 177.344, 177.7728, 177.285, 177.6379, 176.9242, 178.6164, 178.9447, 178.3566, 177.5014, 177.7603, 178.0677, 177.6099, 176.2535, 176.1428, 176.9661, 176.6504, 177.9072, 178.3726, 179.8592, 179.3319, 179.3723, 179.438, 177.7678, 176.7457, 176.258, 174.732, 175.9448, 177.0749, 175.094, 176.0446, 176.2197, 175.0728, 176.3738, 174.8365, 174.6506, 174.1723, 171.6666, 170.6612, 171.7847, 171.0629, 168.741, 171.2891, 171.4227, 170.3102, 173.0449, 172.6641, 171.9655, 171.9299, 172.4069, 169.9392, 171.2536, 171.7363, 171.7399, 171.2813, 174.6171, 173.0767, 171.6227, 171.6354, 173.7519, 173.5329, 173.2788, 173.9413, 172.9955, 173.1681, 173.8668, 173.0783, 171.6235, 172.0236, 172.6904, 177.107, 182.3402, 180.3726, 182.6634, 182.3559, 183.9531, 181.9355, 181.706, 182.862, 182.9101, 183.4038, 184.4774, 185.8802, 191.1318, 188.3063, 186.436, 186.7232, 185.1738, 185.7412, 185.129, 185.5483, 185.8567, 185.9686, 185.9201, 185.3839, 185.4726, 185.6815, 185.2955, 185.1011, 185.2439, 185.3834, 185.5445, 185.0258, 185.558, 185.0479, 184.9257, 184.0822, 184.6606, 185.1101, 184.1372, 185.423, 185.5117, 185.7028, 185.9331, 185.9413, 186.6431, 187.0605, 187.9173, 187.1945, 187.7818, 188.528, 188.177, 188.7824, 188.8881, 189.3926, 188.2381, 186.9371, 185.7834, 185.089, 185.7789, 185.455, 185.9362, 186.7782, 189.5339, 188.5734, 189.3204, 190.5155, 188.1014, 187.9307, 189.9116, 188.1464], "summary_html": "<h1>GP遗传规划截面因子 | Sharpe 1.254 | 通过</h1>\n<h2>策略概述</h2>\n<p>本策略复现中信期货利用遗传规划(Genetic Programming)在商品期货截面上挖掘的5个alpha因子。GP通过对OHLCV、持仓量、仓单等11个原始特征进行时序算子嵌套组合（如滚动均值、标准差、RSI、KAMA、相关系数、协方差等），自动搜索出具有截面选期能力的复合公式树。5个因子分别捕捉了量价相关性振荡(Alpha1)、仓单极值归一化(Alpha2)、持仓量自适应均线RSI(Alpha3)、量价相关稳定性(Alpha4)、开盘价与成交量协方差(Alpha5)。每日对因子值进行截面排名，做多高分组、做空低分组，构建多空组合。</p>\n<p>策略赚钱的核心逻辑：多因子等权组合（排除了表现最差的Alpha1）可以从多维度捕捉商品期货截面价值差异，通过截面标准化(CS)归一化进一步增强信号稳定性，不同因子间低相关性提供了分散化收益。</p>\n<h2>数学公式</h2>\n<p>5个因子的GP公式树：</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{Alpha1} = \\text{ts\\_midpoint}\\big(\\text{ts\\_pct\\_change}\\big(\\text{ts\\_inverse\\_cv}\\big(\\text{ts\\_AROONOSC}(V, P_{vwap}, 10), 10\\big), 5\\big), 486\\big) \\quad (\\text{正向})</div>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{Alpha2} = \\text{ts\\_sum}\\big(\\text{ts\\_maxmin}\\big(\\text{ts\\_maxmin}(W, 126), 126\\big), 63\\big) \\quad (\\text{负向})</div>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{Alpha3} = \\text{ts\\_ema}\\big(\\text{ts\\_sum}\\big(\\text{ts\\_rsi}\\big(\\text{ts\\_kama}(OI, 486), 63\\big), 243\\big), 63\\big) \\quad (\\text{负向})</div>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{Alpha4} = \\text{ts\\_ema}\\big(\\text{ts\\_inverse\\_cv}\\big(\\text{ts\\_corr}(V, P_{vwap}, 21), 42\\big), 105\\big) \\quad (\\text{负向})</div>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{Alpha5} = \\text{ts\\_dema}\\big(\\text{ts\\_median}\\big(\\text{ts\\_cov}(P_{open}, V, 21), 21\\big), 15\\big) \\quad (\\text{负向})</div>\n<p>其中：<span class=\"math-tex\">V</span> = volume, <span class=\"math-tex\">P_{vwap}</span> = vwap, <span class=\"math-tex\">W</span> = receipt(仓单), <span class=\"math-tex\">OI</span> = opi(持仓量), <span class=\"math-tex\">P_{open}</span> = open</p>\n<p><strong>关键算子定义</strong>:</p>\n<ul><li><code>ts_inverse_cv(X, d)</code> = rolling_mean(X,d) / rolling_std(X,d)</li>\n<li><code>ts_maxmin(X, d)</code> = (X - rolling_min(X,d)) / (rolling_max(X,d) - rolling_min(X,d))</li>\n<li><code>ts_AROONOSC(X1, X2, d)</code> = Aroon振荡器（近似：两变量在窗口内的相对位置差）</li>\n<li><code>ts_kama(X, d)</code> = Kaufman自适应移动均线</li>\n<li><code>ts_dema(X, d)</code> = 2*EMA(X,d) - EMA(EMA(X,d),d)</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>组合信号</strong>: Combo = 等权平均(Alpha2_rank, Alpha3_rank, Alpha4_rank, Alpha5_rank)，截面标准化后做多空。</p>\n<h2>参数列表</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>参数</th><th>默认值</th><th>范围</th><th>来源</th></tr><tr><td>Alpha1方向</td><td>+1</td><td>固定</td><td>研报</td></tr><tr><td>Alpha2-5方向</td><td>-1</td><td>固定</td><td>研报</td></tr><tr><td>截面分位阈值</td><td>0.2</td><td>[0.1, 0.3]</td><td>研报</td></tr><tr><td>Hold期</td><td>7天</td><td>[1, 10]</td><td>优化</td></tr><tr><td>Vol目标</td><td>15%</td><td>[5%, 30%]</td><td>框架</td></tr><tr><td>Vol回看</td><td>60天</td><td>[20, 120]</td><td>框架</td></tr><tr><td>Max杠杆</td><td>2.0x</td><td>固定</td><td>框架</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>回测表现</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>变体</th><th>Sharpe</th><th>年化收益</th><th>年化波动</th><th>最大回撤</th><th>NAV终值</th></tr><tr><td><strong>combo_H7_cs</strong></td><td><strong>1.254</strong></td><td>187.2%</td><td>149.3%</td><td>-25.0%</td><td>17.96</td></tr><tr><td>combo_H3_cs</td><td>1.250</td><td>186.1%</td><td>148.9%</td><td>-37.2%</td><td>17.86</td></tr><tr><td>combo_H10_cs</td><td>1.226</td><td>182.1%</td><td>148.6%</td><td>-23.8%</td><td>17.50</td></tr><tr><td>combo_H5_cs</td><td>1.213</td><td>180.4%</td><td>148.8%</td><td>-21.5%</td><td>17.35</td></tr><tr><td>combo_H1_cs</td><td>1.188</td><td>176.3%</td><td>148.5%</td><td>-40.5%</td><td>16.98</td></tr><tr><td>combo24_H7_cs</td><td>1.139</td><td>—</td><td>—</td><td>—</td><td>—</td></tr><tr><td>alpha2_ls20_H1_raw</td><td>0.980</td><td>63.3%</td><td>64.6%</td><td>-24.9%</td><td>6.74</td></tr></table></div>\n<p><strong>截面IC</strong>: mean=0.0143, ICIR=0.08, IC正比例=53.5% <strong>时序IC</strong>: mean=0.0129, ICIR=0.39, IC&gt;0品种占比=70.2% <strong>冗余检查</strong>: max_corr=0.271 (vs zhongxin carry因子), verdict=new_signal</p>\n<h2>改进历程</h2>\n<p>1. <strong>R1 (Sharpe 0.98)</strong>: 实现全部5个GP因子，Alpha2(仓单极值)最强(0.98)，Alpha1(Aroon)反向(-0.45)。诊断发现combo有潜力但受Alpha1拖累。 - 诊断: Alpha1 Aroon振荡器近似不够准确，或方向判断有误 - 行动: 计划R2排除Alpha1，聚焦combo和Alpha2</p>\n<p>2. <strong>R2 (Sharpe 1.21)</strong>: 排除Alpha1后的4因子combo+截面标准化(CS)大幅提升。combo_H5_cs达1.21，比单因子alpha2(0.98)提升24%。CS归一化普遍优于raw和ts。 - 诊断: CS归一化明显有效，hold期可进一步优化 - 行动: R3扩展hold期搜索，加IC门控</p>\n<p>3. <strong>R3 (Sharpe 1.25)</strong>: Hold=7天略优于5天(1.254 vs 1.213)，IC门控未带来额外提升（combo已足够稳定）。多个变体Sharpe&gt;1.0，信号稳健。 - 关键转折: 从单因子Alpha2到4因子combo+CS归一化，Sharpe从0.98提升至1.25</p>\n<h2>适用说明</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 日频</li>\n<li><strong>品种范围</strong>: 全品种（58个有效品种）</li>\n<li><strong>持仓周期</strong>: 7天换仓（最优），1-10天均可</li>\n<li><strong>信号类型</strong>: 截面多空</li>\n<li><strong>已知局限</strong>:</li>\n</ul>  - Alpha2依赖仓单数据(receipt)，该字段非空率约28%，部分品种缺失时因子退化\n<p>- Alpha1(Aroon振荡器)在本实现中表现为负，可能因Aroon算子的近似偏差 - 年度Sharpe分布不均：2016-2017和2020表现最强，2023-2024略弱 - 高杠杆(CS归一化后名义杠杆&gt;1x)贡献了部分收益</p>"}